<!here|@here> update on our production-upgraded Cubby:

"We have installed all of the new parts and have tested / confirmed video, touch, and motion are working as expected. 

Right now, we have some additional detailing for the cubby interior and need to sort out the LEDs. We also want to do more testing out the open / close prior to ship -- it's whisper quiet now!"
also, check out new folder on gDrive meant to house photos/info on NYC Space.  I just uploaded Ewald’s photos of NYC space from last week
Reminder: if you’re working on the BL 2016 Onboarding JIRA project please post updates to your status (with ticket numbers if relevant)

<!here|@here> Working this week on getting docs updated with the remaining content, and revising what’s in there. Got set up to run the VR flow so I can throw some updates from Felix in it and kick the tires a bit. Good news: was up and running in 10 mins.
